external_knowledge:
- 'prolific organizations' refers to organizations that have given more than 100 total hours (o.total_hours_given > 100); 
- 'actively giving back' refers to organizations that have conducted transactions within the last year (t.trans_date >= DATE('now', '-1 year')); 
- 'actively giving back' also implies that organizations have at least one distinct transaction ID (COUNT(DISTINCT t.trans_id) > 0).
